702295f-a.text:
3rd Avenue, north from 37th Street, showing the Bush Terminal buildings. On the east side of the avenue can be seen construction
work on the Gowanus Parkway.
View 2 shows 37th Street houses.
P. L. Sperr  January, 1941
Views 1,2
